# CodeQL ignore file for monorepo-wide analysis

# Build output directories
**/bin/**
**/obj/**

# NuGet and dependency caches
**/.nuget/**
**/node_modules/**

# Razor generated files
**/*.razor.g.cs
**/*.razor.g.css

# Test and coverage artifacts
**/TestResults/**
**/coverage/**

# Temporary and IDE artifacts
**/*.tmp
**/.vs/**

# Generated web assets
**/service-worker-assets.js
